data.description:
Well maintained and spacious FIVE bedroom vinyl sided bungalow with two full baths, recreation room, spacious living room, formal dining area and central air. If you have a growing or large family, this is the home for you.  There are three bedrooms on the first floor, living room-dining room combination with beautiful hardwood floor.  The kitchen is bright and has eating area and plenty of cabinets.   The upstairs has two spacious bedrooms and a sitting-computer-gaming area.  This is a great lovingly cared for home on a great street.  Take a look, you won't be disappointed.  
Subject to seller finding a new home.
